description: We sampled global bottom up proteomics data from 48 diverse bacteria and searched for sites of lysine acetylation. Bacteria came from 6 phyla: proteobacteria, cyanobacteria, firmicutes, bacteroidetes, actinobacteria, and fibrobacteres.
